author: @dianadennis7225
text: Would love to see some YTD, QTD, MTD, custom periods, etc., how to switch views from, say, YTD to MTD, and, in general, more complex use cases of Tableau. I m using these a lot at work, and I wish I had known them when I started out. Drag and drop won't cut it; the power of Tableau is understanding calculated fields & LOD & param. If you want a job in this field, those are a must.
